OL,3,C'It's excluding': Jersey's ice rink
OL,4,Cunder scrutiny for lack of
OL,5,Caccessibility
OL,7,FJersey's Ice Rink is under scrutiny
OL,8,Fafter issues have been raised about
OL,9,Fthe lack of accessibility.
OL,11,FThis comes after residents raised the
OL,12,Fissue of no sit-on karts, which
OL,13,Fpreviously allowed islanders with
OL,14,Fdisabilities to use the ice rink.
OL,16,FHowever, Jersey Development Company
OL,17,Fwhich operates the rink, stated the
OL,18,Fkarts had been withdrawn this year
OL,19,Fbecause of misuse by non-disabled
OL,20,Fusers and safety concerns.
