OL,3,C'It's excluding': Jersey's ice rink
OL,4,Cunder scrutiny for lack of
OL,5,Caccessibility
OL,7,FJames Bedding, an islander raising
OL,8,Faccessibility concerns, was 15 when he
OL,9,Ffell from the harbour wall in St.
OL,10,FHelier, leaving him paralysed.
OL,12,FHe says this news is disappointing, he
OL,13,Fexplains: "It's excluding. It excludes
OL,14,Flots of people with disabilities, not
OL,15,Fallowing them to be involved or have
OL,16,Fthe correct facilities to enjoy these
OL,17,Fevents, it is a huge disappointment
OL,18,Fand you do feel excluded.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
