OL,3,C'It's excluding': Jersey's ice rink
OL,4,Cunder scrutiny for lack of
OL,5,Caccessibility
OL,7,F"It's a huge disappointment to find
OL,8,Fout it's not going to be accessible
OL,9,Ffor someone who needs these
OL,10,Ffacilities. I feel for so many younger
OL,11,Fpeople and families."
OL,13,FHe adds: "We noticed that the disabled
OL,14,Ftoilets are not included inside the
OL,15,Fice rink, so you have got the able-
OL,16,Fbodied toilets male and female inside,
OL,17,Fbut anyone in a wheelchair or who has
OL,18,Fa disability who needs to access a
OL,19,Ftoilet, needs to go outside of the
OL,20,Frink to go and use a portaloo."
