OL,3,C'It's excluding': Jersey's ice rink
OL,4,Cunder scrutiny for lack of
OL,5,Caccessibility
OL,7,FSean Pontin, Chief Officer of the
OL,8,Fdisability charity Enable Jersey,
OL,9,Fsays: "I think it is very sad that we
OL,10,Fare having this conversation today, it
OL,11,Fis 2024."
OL,13,FHe adds: "It is beyond belief and it
OL,14,Fis very sad that we are having this
OL,15,Fconversation.
OL,17,F"Some of the comments that we have
OL,18,Fread on social media are what we would
OL,19,Fsay as an organisation, is quite
OL,20,Fdisgraceful.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
