OL,3,C'It's excluding': Jersey's ice rink
OL,4,Cunder scrutiny for lack of
OL,5,Caccessibility
OL,7,F"If you look at the ice rink, we have
OL,8,Fa blue portaloo at the front when
OL,9,Fanybody else can use the facilities
OL,10,Finside.
OL,12,F"I don't know what that says, but I'm
OL,13,Fsure if we spoke to people with a
OL,14,Fdisability I know what they would be
OL,15,Fsaying, and I don't think any other
OL,16,Fminority group on the island would be
OL,17,Ftreated that way."
