OL,4,Cunder scrutiny for lack of
OL,5,Caccessibility
OL,7,FIn response, Lee Henry, Chief Officer
OL,8,Fof Jersey Development Company, says:
OL,9,F"The ice rink is fully accessible and
OL,10,Finclusive. The karts, which were
OL,11,Fbananas last year, were quickly
OL,12,Fwithdrawn from open use because of
OL,13,Fhealth and safety concerns.
OL,15,F"They are also not a disability aid,
OL,16,Fso from a health and safety
OL,17,Fperspective and if there was an
OL,18,Faccident on those bananas, they are
OL,19,Fnot meant for any disability support."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
