OL,7,FHowever, he says it has not been
OL,8,Fdisregarded, he says: "We are looking
OL,9,Finto what other provision could be
OL,10,Fmade to support disabled islanders
OL,11,Fusing the ice rink and we also have an
OL,12,Finvitation for non-motorised
OL,13,Fwheelchairs to access the rink.
OL,15,F"Last Saturday we had someone in their
OL,16,Fnon-motorised wheelchair come and use
OL,17,Fthe rink and we are looking into
OL,18,Fadditional equipment that we can have
OL,19,Favailable at the rink, so if a
OL,20,Fcustomer came in a motorised
OL,21,Fwheelchair, we can support them."
